# Dash pages

- Build layout with helpers from `app/components/ui.py` (`app_shell`, `section_panel`, charts, tables, cards).
- New routes require a branch in `app/main.py` `route` callback and a renderer under `app/pages/`.
- Keep copy and structure aligned with the regime-first product (Overview, Markets, Watchlist, Ticker).
- Prefer passing snapshot/dataclass models from services rather than fetching inside page modules.
